entries.name: foaf:Agent
entries.description: An agent (eg. person, group, software or physical artifact).

entries.name: foaf:Document
entries.description: A document.

entries.name: foaf:Group
entries.description: A class of Agents.

entries.name: foaf:Image
entries.description: An image.

entries.name: foaf:LabelProperty
entries.description: A foaf:LabelProperty is any RDF property with texual values that serve as labels.

entries.name: foaf:OnlineAccount
entries.description: An online account.

entries.name: foaf:OnlineChatAccount
entries.description: An online chat account.

entries.name: foaf:OnlineEcommerceAccount
entries.description: An online e-commerce account.

entries.name: foaf:OnlineGamingAccount
entries.description: An online gaming account.

entries.name: foaf:Organization
entries.description: An organization.

entries.name: foaf:Person
entries.description: A person.

entries.name: foaf:PersonalProfileDocument
entries.description: A personal profile RDF document.

entries.name: foaf:Project
entries.description: A project (a collective endeavour of some kind).

entries.name: foaf:account
entries.description: Indicates an account held by this agent.

entries.name: foaf:accountName
entries.description: Indicates the name (identifier) associated with this online account.

entries.name: foaf:accountServiceHomepage
entries.description: Indicates a homepage of the service provide for this online account.

entries.name: foaf:age
entries.description: The age in years of some agent.

entries.name: foaf:aimChatID
entries.description: An AIM chat ID

entries.name: foaf:based_near
entries.description: A location that something is based near, for some broadly human notion of near.

entries.name: foaf:birthday
entries.description: The birthday of this Agent, represented in mm-dd string form, eg. '12-31'.

entries.name: foaf:currentProject
entries.description: A current project this person works on.

entries.name: foaf:depiction
entries.description: A depiction of some thing.

entries.name: foaf:depicts
entries.description: A thing depicted in this representation.

entries.name: foaf:dnaChecksum
entries.description: A checksum for the DNA of some thing. Joke.

entries.name: foaf:familyName
entries.description: The family name of some person.

entries.name: foaf:family_name
entries.description: The family name of some person.

entries.name: foaf:firstName
entries.description: The first name of a person.

entries.name: foaf:focus
entries.description: The underlying or 'focal' entity associated with some SKOS-described concept.

entries.name: foaf:fundedBy
entries.description: An organization funding a project or person.

entries.name: foaf:geekcode
entries.description: A textual geekcode for this person, see http://www.geekcode.com/geek.html

entries.name: foaf:gender
entries.description: The gender of this Agent (typically but not necessarily 'male' or 'female').

entries.name: foaf:givenName
entries.description: The given name of some person.

entries.name: foaf:givenname
entries.description: The given name of some person.

entries.name: foaf:holdsAccount
entries.description: Indicates an account held by this agent.

entries.name: foaf:homepage
entries.description: A homepage for some thing.

entries.name: foaf:icqChatID
entries.description: An ICQ chat ID

entries.name: foaf:img
entries.description: An image that can be used to represent some thing (ie. those depictions which are particularly representative of something, eg. one's photo on a homepage).

entries.name: foaf:interest
entries.description: A page about a topic of interest to this person.

entries.name: foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf
entries.description: A document that this thing is the primary topic of.

entries.name: foaf:jabberID
entries.description: A jabber ID for something.

entries.name: foaf:knows
entries.description: A person known by this person (indicating some level of reciprocated interaction between the parties).

entries.name: foaf:lastName
entries.description: The last name of a person.

entries.name: foaf:logo
entries.description: A logo representing some thing.

entries.name: foaf:made
entries.description: Something that was made by this agent.

entries.name: foaf:maker
entries.description: An agent that  made this thing.

entries.name: foaf:mbox
entries.description: A  personal mailbox, ie. an Internet mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the first owner of this mailbox. This is a 'static inverse functional property', in that  there is (across time and change) at most one individual that ever has any particular value for foaf:mbox.

entries.name: foaf:mbox_sha1sum
entries.description: The sha1sum of the URI of an Internet mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the  first owner of the mailbox.

entries.name: foaf:member
entries.description: Indicates a member of a Group

entries.name: foaf:membershipClass
entries.description: Indicates the class of individuals that are a member of a Group

entries.name: foaf:msnChatID
entries.description: An MSN chat ID

entries.name: foaf:myersBriggs
entries.description: A Myers Briggs (MBTI) personality classification.

entries.name: foaf:name
entries.description: A name for some thing.

entries.name: foaf:nick
entries.description: A short informal nickname characterising an agent (includes login identifiers, IRC and other chat nicknames).

entries.name: foaf:openid
entries.description: An OpenID for an Agent.

entries.name: foaf:page
entries.description: A page or document about this thing.

entries.name: foaf:pastProject
entries.description: A project this person has previously worked on.

entries.name: foaf:phone
entries.description: A phone,  specified using fully qualified tel: URI scheme (refs: http://www.w3.org/Addressing/schemes.html#tel).

entries.name: foaf:plan
entries.description: A .plan comment, in the tradition of finger and '.plan' files.

entries.name: foaf:primaryTopic
entries.description: The primary topic of some page or document.

entries.name: foaf:publications
entries.description: A link to the publications of this person.

entries.name: foaf:schoolHomepage
entries.description: A homepage of a school attended by the person.

entries.name: foaf:sha1
entries.description: A sha1sum hash, in hex.

entries.name: foaf:skypeID
entries.description: A Skype ID

entries.name: foaf:status
entries.description: A string expressing what the user is happy for the general public (normally) to know about their current activity.

entries.name: foaf:surname
entries.description: The surname of some person.

entries.name: foaf:theme
entries.description: A theme.

entries.name: foaf:thumbnail
entries.description: A derived thumbnail image.

entries.name: foaf:tipjar
entries.description: A tipjar document for this agent, describing means for payment and reward.

entries.name: foaf:title
entries.description: Title (Mr, Mrs, Ms, Dr. etc)

entries.name: foaf:topic
entries.description: A topic of some page or document.

entries.name: foaf:topic_interest
entries.description: A thing of interest to this person.

entries.name: foaf:weblog
entries.description: A weblog of some thing (whether person, group, company etc.).

entries.name: foaf:workInfoHomepage
entries.description: A work info homepage of some person; a page about their work for some organization.

entries.name: foaf:workplaceHomepage
entries.description: A workplace homepage of some person; the homepage of an organization they work for.

entries.name: foaf:yahooChatID
entries.description: A Yahoo chat ID
